TITLE.P: Framework Agreement for the provision of Property & Valuation Services

SHORT_DESCR.P: The purpose of this RFT is to establish a framework agreement for the provision of the following:
1) General services and valuation advice as may typically be provided by auctioneers for lands and property,
2) Valuation, acquisition and disposal services lands, properties and items other than art and collectibles,
3) Valuation and disposal services for art and collectibles,
4) Auctioneering Services for the Letting of Land.
